parameters: Wait, am I Stripes or Solids?
I feel like I should’ve dressed up...
Ya like it? Ah didn’t know what exactly t’ wear,
but it seemed like it’d fit in with a dive like this...
I really like it... I mean, in terms of looks you are
light years away from anything that would fit into this
Your pussy can do whatever it wants with my tongue...
Hot damn yer quick... Lemme get you a drink.
I was gonna say at least you’re on theme for here, y’know?
Cowboy bar, jukebox, whiskey... You fit right in.
You wanna take a ride on the bull?
Is that what we’re callin’ yer friend these days?
I might need a few more drinks
Nobody knows if it was a drug deal gone bad or what...
They ain’t never heard from him again, man just up an’
That’s crazy, they never found out what happened,
like why he did it or where he ran off to?
Nah... Wild stuff like that happens
Folks said somethin’ about money bein’ owed,
but if any of em’ know they ain’t talkin’... I’d guess no
one really knows except for the dead and the gone...
You’ve lived quite the life out there...
Do you ever miss the country?
Sometimes. There’s a lot more opportunity here,
an’ I grew up in Vesper, but I did build a life out there,
had a little bar - nicer than this place...
Oh, I didn’t know you had a bar!
Yeah, we had a still an’ made our own whiskey.
Most popular waterin’ hole in town, Brandy started
workin’ behind the bar when she was old enough an’...
Nuthin important, Tiger... Ain’t nothing that lasts forever,
an’ we ain’t doing so bad back here...
I have to say I’m happy you’re here...
Dammit, Ah wish you weren’t mah sister’s kid...
I know. It... Complicates our situation.
Yer a good guy, an’ I deserve to have some fun every
now an’ then - why do Ah I have to feel like I’m
stabbing Les in the back doin’ it?
You definitely do deserve to be happy, Aunt Cass...
I’m sorry for making things... How they are.
I’m a grown woman, everythin’s as
much mah fault as yours, Tiger.
Ah think... I’m just about drunk
You ride too, an’ whoever holds on the longest...
*Hic* This’ll be fun... Gets t’ pick their prize.
Whatever yer little heart desires, Tiger... You in?
Alright, whoever stays on the longest, wins!
Dang it, I’m outta practice... Yer up, Tiger.
<Hide Button Console><center>Try to beat Cassie's time
- MASH Enter to fill the bar and keep your balance! -
Not even close... Ain’t *hic* used t’ holding
onto somethin’ buckin’ that hard on ya?
I guess not, maybe you could help me practice?
Ha! I won, remember? You gotta do what I want.
Dang, thought I had you... So, what do you want me to do?
Hm... I don’t wanna be too mean to ya,
ya *hic* did go for the ride after all...
You... Gotta carry me home tonight.
Carry you?? That’s all the way across town!
Lot of time to work on that grip, then...
How the *hic*... Heck did you hold on that long?
I know what I’d like it to be...
things we can’t do... Yer Mom...
I know... OK, well then, since I clearly
know what I’m doing on the bull...
I give you a personal lesson on riding?
You still talkin’ the machine... Or you, Tiger?
Feel like this saddle got a lot more cushion all
of a sudden... You doing ok, Aunt Cass?
Hah - hah- I'm doin'... hah - fine, Tiger..!
Good, I think I wanna keep this
ride going for a long time!
This place is fun, in a kitschy kind of way.
I've had one bourbon... an' one shot... but I think if
I order a beer... I'm gonna pass out...
